Crystal Abilities

Crystal abilities will becomes available for use according to the number of crystals you've completed by unlocking all spaces for a given color.

Crystal abilities are command abilities the party can use. Each crystal ability requires a certain amount of crystal power.

■Crystal Power

Crystal power will be displayed in battle after obtaining a crystal ability. Using a crystal ability consumes crystal power. The amount of crystal power available at the start of battle will increase with the number of crystals completed in the crystal room.

■Individual Crystal Abilities

The effects of crystal abilities that become available with completed crystals are as follows:
  • 1 color complete: Crystal Ability – Attack BRV attack + HP attack (consumes certain amount of HP damage bonus) Force time duration does not decrease at time of ability use
  • 2 colors complete: Crystal Ability – Defend Party becomes unable to act for certain period in exchange for immunity to actions, including those that would KO Force time duration does not decrease at time of ability use
  • 3 colors complete: Crystal Ability – Speed Certain number of selected allies may exchange turn order with the ally at the head of turn order Turn rate for ally at head of turn order becomes instantaneous for certain number of turns Force time duration does not decrease at time of ability use
  • 4 colors complete: Crystal Ability – Heal Restores party's HP, revives fallen allies Boosts party's stats for certain number of turns Force time duration does not decrease at time of ability use
  • 5 colors complete: Crystal Ability – Reflect Reduces own HP damage, BRV damage taken for certain number of turns HP damage is reflected onto enemy (ignores effects that change HP damage) Reduces own HP damage dealt Force time duration does not decrease at time of ability use
  • 6 colors complete: Crystal Ability – Dominate Deals HP damage to all enemies based on target's MAX HP (ignores effects that change HP damage) Force time duration does not decrease at time of ability use
